clear all;
close all;
nn=900; %%% nombre de points par classe
oiseau1 = importdata('C:\Users\hp\Desktop\TL\Apprentissage\featuresoiseau1.txt');
oiseau1 = oiseau1(1:nn,:);
oiseau2 = importdata('C:\Users\hp\Desktop\TL\Apprentissage\featuresoiseau2.txt');
oiseau2 = oiseau2(1:nn,:);
oiseau3 = importdata('C:\Users\hp\Desktop\TL\Apprentissage\featuresoiseau3.txt');
oiseau3 = oiseau3(1:nn,:);
%%% classe 1
cl1_d1=oiseau1(:,1)';
cl1_d2=oiseau1(:,2)';
%%% classe 3
cl2_d1=oiseau2(:,1)';
cl2_d2=oiseau2(:,2)';
%%% classe 4
cl3_d1=oiseau3(:,1)';
cl3_d2=oiseau3(:,2)';
%%% normalisation des 2 features en moyenne et en écart-type
moy1=mean([cl1_d1 cl2_d1 cl3_d1]);
moy2=mean([cl1_d2 cl2_d2 cl3_d2]);
std1=std([cl1_d1 cl2_d1 cl3_d1]);
std2=std([cl1_d2 cl2_d2 cl3_d2]);
cl1_d1=(cl1_d1-moy1)/std1;
cl1_d2=(cl1_d2-moy2)/std2;
cl2_d1=(cl2_d1-moy1)/std1;
cl2_d2=(cl2_d2-moy2)/std2;
cl3_d1=(cl3_d1-moy1)/std1;
cl3_d2=(cl3_d2-moy2)/std2;
%%% les 2 paramètres SVM à régler
sig2=0.3; %% 0.3 semble pas mal
nu=0.01;
figure(1);
clf;
grid on;
hold on;
plot(cl1_d1,cl1_d2,'or');
plot(cl2_d1,cl2_d2,'*b');
plot(cl3_d1,cl3_d2,'+g');
hold off;

Apprentissage du SVM

%% 1er SVM : cl1 versus cl2+cl3
fprintf(1,'-----> classe1 versus classe2 + classe3\n');
-----> classe1 versus classe2 + classe3
nn1=nn;
nn2=nn+nn;
donnees1 = [[cl1_d1 cl2_d1 cl3_d1]' [cl1_d2 cl2_d2 cl3_d2]']'; %%% données
classes1 = [ones(1,nn1) -ones(1,nn2)]; %%% labels des 2 classes
[alphaloqo1,yloqo1,bbbopt1] = uncontretousoutil(donnees1,nn1,nn2,classes1,sig2,nu);

temps requis pour LOQO : 26.498000
tmpv2_3 = alphaloqo3.*classes3';
%%% pavage du plan, pour montrer les frontières entre les 3 classes
nzz=500;
mind1c=min(donnees1(1,:))-0.0;
maxd1c=max(donnees1(1,:))+0.0;
pasd1=(maxd1c-mind1c)/nzz;
mind2c=min(donnees1(2,:))-0.0;
maxd2c=max(donnees1(2,:))+0.0;
pasd2=(maxd2c-mind2c)/nzz;
ppd1res = [];
ppd2res = [];
ppd1=mind1c;
for ii=1:nzz
ppd2=mind2c;
for jj=1:nzz
clnew1 = tmpv2_1'*lagis_rbf_gaussien([ppd1 ppd2]', donnees1, sig2)' + bbbopt1;
clnew2 = tmpv2_2'*lagis_rbf_gaussien([ppd1 ppd2]', donnees2, sig2)' + bbbopt2;
clnew3 = tmpv2_3'*lagis_rbf_gaussien([ppd1 ppd2]', donnees3, sig2)' + bbbopt3;
m = max([clnew1,clnew2,clnew3]);
if m == clnew1
clnew(ii,jj)=1;
elseif m == clnew2
clnew(ii,jj)=0;
elseif m == clnew3
clnew(ii,jj)=-1;
% if clnew1>clnew2 && clnew1>clnew3
% clnew(ii,jj)=1;
% elseif clnew2>clnew1 && clnew2>clnew3
% clnew(ii,jj)=0;
% elseif clnew3>clnew1 && clnew3>clnew2
% clnew(ii,jj)=-1;
else
fprintf(1,'probleme\n');
end;
if ii==1
ppd2res=[ppd2res ppd2];
end;
ppd2=ppd2+pasd2;
end;
ppd1res=[ppd1res ppd1];
ppd1=ppd1+pasd1;
end;
%%% plot pour la route
figure(7);
clf;
title('frontiere entre les 3 classes');

Calcul de l'erreur d'apprentissage
error = 0;
for i=1:length(donnees1(1,:))
clnew1 = tmpv2_1'*lagis_rbf_gaussien([donnees1(1,i) donnees1(2,i)]', donnees1, sig2)' + bbbopt1;
clnew2 = tmpv2_2'*lagis_rbf_gaussien([donnees1(1,i) donnees1(2,i)]', donnees2, sig2)' + bbbopt2;
clnew3 = tmpv2_3'*lagis_rbf_gaussien([donnees1(1,i) donnees1(2,i)]', donnees3, sig2)' + bbbopt3;
m = [clnew1,clnew2,clnew3];
[argvalue, argmax] = max(m);
if i<=nn && not(argmax == 1)
error = error + 1;
elseif i>nn && i<=2*nn && not(argmax == 2)
error = error + 1;
elseif i>2*nn && not(argmax == 3)
error = error + 1;
end;
end
learning_error_rate = 100*error/(3*nn)
learning_error_rate = 8.3333
fprintf('the learning error rate %4.2f %%', learning_error_rate)
